{"tid":599533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【車Cam直擊】寶馬直鏟行人路 撞好媽媽一刻曝光","createTime":"2018-03-20T13:25:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T01:10:50.000Z","uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fe3f817cefc067e28e84da49389d38f184c66735","tid":599533,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T13:25:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180320/57973458\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180320%2F57973458&d=al32BsPKWMQRvAALuvaY6gdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=ccfbd4c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180320%2F57973458&h=ed351957\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180320/57973458</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180320/large/1521549545_6ee2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180320%2Flarge%2F1521549545_6ee2.jpg&h=1d2ba412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨晨手抱兩歲女兒的姓杜婦人，在葵涌梨樹路遭一輛失事鏟上行人路的寶馬房車撞斷雙腳，《蘋果》取得該宗恐怖車禍的第一時間現場車Cam片，片段中所見當時寶馬的車速不高，但司機似乎一路直駛，未察覺寶馬應要扭軑右轉；結果寶馬鏟上行人路把好媽媽撞倒，並將她推向燈箱始停下。<br />\n<br />\n片段由一輛尾隨寶馬的私家車車Cam拍得，從片中所見，當時涉事寶馬沿梨樹路上斜，寶馬前方有一輛貨車，兩車車速正常，不是太快，但寶馬駛至上址近小巴站時，司機應要扭軑右轉，但不知為何卻失控直駛上行人路撞及交通燈控制箱，並將行人路上手抱BB的杜婦撞倒。事後寶馬司機下車查看杜婦傷勢。<br />\n<br />\n杜婦的胞姊今日在醫院表示，有村民目撃寶馬行駛時，司機疑手持手機查閱短訊，懷疑因此肇禍。"},{"pid":"9a9ddc6fe5d24fadca67ad4522a42619df65751e","tid":599533,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T13:29:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"17c52373fdd4fdcc76abefdec199b3904365d84c","tid":599533,"uid":1654,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9a9ddc6fe5d24fadca67ad4522a42619df65751e","tid":599533,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T13:29:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T13:31:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁就可以加分？"},{"pid":"0e159fe7ba80220891eca84cc7a73974258574d7","tid":599533,"uid":45934,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9a9ddc6fe5d24fadca67ad4522a42619df65751e","tid":599533,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T13:29:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T13:32:53.000Z","msg":"做錯左事事後點補求都冇用<br />\n<br />\n我自己揸車就係同自己講一絲心浮氣燥都中唔可以有<br />\n為嘅就係一生都未必會出現一次嘅意外"},{"pid":"8237b509900673cc4966c786cc2b2fbae54bcd6c","tid":599533,"uid":294,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T23:11:53.000Z","msg":"根本無轉過呔"},{"pid":"b90826252e400750a2a07ab2f36246d48516cf3f","tid":599533,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T23:14:46.000Z","msg":"用緊電話！有類似Tesla 自動駕駛系統就唔會發生"},{"pid":"99ca89012c2e99d2fd31a14747732f3bb244cb88","tid":599533,"uid":97814,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T23:39:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f219b878e25c0a87d775d177d7ee40907b73221d","tid":599533,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T23:50:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d71adc31e14e243838a2713eb4a9c28a974b6951","tid":599533,"uid":759,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f219b878e25c0a87d775d177d7ee40907b73221d","tid":599533,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T23:50:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T00:00:28.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b2530cc07756e8d58a8c6ceec2db332c3c82d7","tid":599533,"uid":88029,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T00:03:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"faef0707f8b51b53e7fecf7ac14c23ebd004f78b","tid":599